Lycanroc (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0744: Rockruff
Pokémon
#0746: Wishiwashi →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Lycanroc (TCG Pocket).

Lycanroc has been featured on 19 different cards since it debuted as one of the SM Black Star Promos of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Lycanroc cards are normally Fighting-type Stage 1 Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Lycanroc

Lycanroc
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
